**Job Description \& Summary**
 Join our cutting\-edge development team, where you will play a pivotal role in building next\-generation web applications powered by modern frameworks and AI\-driven capabilities. You’ll leverage technologies like Python, FastAPI, React, PostgreSQL, Azure AI Search, and GenAI to create scalable, secure, and high\-performing solutions. Whether designing intuitive user interfaces, implementing complex backend logic, or integrating advanced AI features such as RAG\-based search and intelligent agents, your expertise will shape the future of digital experiences for our clients.




**This Is What You'll Do**
 As an Experienced Web Application Developer, you will collaborate with multidisciplinary teams, including UX designers, AI specialists, cloud engineers, and business analysts. Your contribution will be key to delivering robust, user\-centric applications that meet business needs and exceed client expectations. Your role will adapt to project requirements, ranging from architectural design to hands\-on coding and deployment.




 Your work environment is dynamic, offering flexibility to work from our office, client sites, or remotely. We invest in continuous learning and innovation, equipping you with the latest tools and methodologies to stay ahead in the fast\-evolving tech landscape.




 Your responsibilities include:




* Designing and developing scalable web applications using Python (FastAPI) and React;
* Implementing secure and optimized data models with PostgreSQL;
* Integrating Azure AI Search and GenAI\-powered features (including RAG pipelines) into applications;
* Applying SOLID principles and best practices in software engineering;
* Creating UML diagrams, wireframes, and technical documentation for system design;
* Building and deploying containerized applications using Docker;
* Collaborating in Scrum teams, using tools like Azure DevOps or Jira for agile delivery;
* Ensuring high\-quality code through version control (Git) and automated testing;
* Bridging communication between technical and non\-technical stakeholders to align solutions with business goals.


**You recognize yourself in this**
 You are passionate about crafting elegant, efficient, and scalable web solutions. You thrive in collaborative environments and enjoy solving complex technical challenges. You combine strong programming skills with a solid understanding of software architecture and design principles.




* You have at least 3 years of experience in web application development;
* Proficiency in Python, FastAPI, React, and PostgreSQL;
* Experience with Azure AI Search, GenAI concepts, and RAG\-based, Agentic AI implementations is a plus;
* Strong grasp of SOLID principles, UML, and software engineering fundamentals;
* Familiarity with Kubernetes, Docker, Scrum, and agile methodologies;
* Ability to design wireframes and translate them into functional applications;
* Skilled in version control systems like Git;
* Strong problem\-solving and analytical skills;
* Fluent in English; Dutch is an advantage.


**What We Offer**
 With us, you’ll have the chance to be yourself, perform at your best in a high\-performance organization, and grow within our global network. We offer you, among other things:




* A competitive salary based on your experience and the opportunity to advance quickly;
* A motivating work environment where collaboration with ambitious colleagues and recognition for your contributions are central;
* A wide range of tailored training focused on professional growth and leadership development;
* Choose the mobility option that suits you best: an electric lease car or a mobility allowance for your business travel costs, plus access to various mobility providers via one convenient app;
* 30 vacation days and the option to purchase additional days;
* At PwC, your well\-being is our priority. That’s why we offer a personal well\-being budget to help you grow in physical and mental health, as well as access to the well\-being platform OpenUp;
* You’ll work on challenging and meaningful client projects, use cutting\-edge technology such as AI tools, learn from the best, and receive support through coaching. Together, we work as an inclusive team to make a real impact;
* Flexibility through hybrid working, including a fully equipped home office and a monthly net expense allowance for internet and other costs.


